From 5ccf721aa9f5e94dce14f6a2de0b9ece1c403de1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 14:20:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Studio2: lessons below cast, fix avatars, smarter button
 states; Library: remove duration filter
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Move LessonEditor to below CharacterCards in the belowCover slot
- CharacterCard: remove voice-avatar fallback so only AI-generated character
  images (or initials) show — no more mismatched voice profile pictures
- Update Script button: stronger active glow/border when directions are pending
- Save Version button: disabled when no unsaved changes, purple accent when active
- Magic Tales (library): remove duration filter chips panel
---
